---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
const lang = 'en';
---
<Layout title="Cookie Policy | Harezm Technology" lang={lang}>
    <div class="pt-32 pb-24 bg-surface min-h-screen">
        <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-8 md:px-0">
            <h1 class="text-4xl font-headline font-bold text-on-background mb-8">Cookie Policy</h1>
            <div class="space-y-6 text-on-surface-variant leading-relaxed font-light">
                <p>When you visit the Harezm site, small data files (cookies) may be saved to your device or browser for performance and essential functionality purposes. The use of cookies on our site is kept at the most minimal, technical level.</p>
                
                <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-on-background mt-10 mb-4">Types of Cookies Used</h2>
                <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2">
                    <li><strong>Strictly Necessary Cookies:</strong> Required for the site to function properly and for remembering your language (TR/EN) and theme (Light/Dark) preferences (e.g., <code>harezm-theme</code>).</li>
                    <li><strong>Performance & Analytics Cookies:</strong> Used for minimal, anonymized measurement to analyze how you use our site. They do not contain advertising or marketing profiling scripts.</li>
                </ul>

                <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-on-background mt-10 mb-4">Controlling Cookie Settings</h2>
                <p>If you do not wish to accept the use of cookies, you can delete or block them from your browser settings. However, in this case, personal interface experiences such as your theme preferences may be reset.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</Layout>
